            <title>[DERBY-1255] Implement new JDBC4 methods for creating empty LOBs in the embedded client</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1255</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement Connection.createClob() and Connection.createBlob(). Right now these methods are implemented in the network client but not the embedded client.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
